`WIZARD`

  The `ai wizard` command initiates interactive step-by-step
  walk thru experiences for various AI services and tools.

  To try it out:
                                                                                                                                        
    TRY: ai wizard

`USAGE`: ai wizard [...]

  AZURE
    --subscription SUBSCRIPTION   (see: ai help wizard subscription)

  RESOURCE
    --region REGION               (see: ai help wizard region)
    --group GROUP                 (see: ai help wizard group)
    --name NAME                   (see: ai help wizard name)

  CHAT
    --model MODEL                 (see: ai help wizard model)
    --deployment DEPLOYMENT       (see: ai help wizard deployment)
    --system PROMPT               (see: ai help wizard system prompt)

  INPUT                           (see: ai help wizard input)
    --file FILE                   (see: ai help wizard file)
    --files PATTERN               (see: ai help wizard files)
    --files @FILELIST.txt         (see: ai help wizard files)
    --jsonl FILE                  (see: ai help wizard jsonl)

  SCENARIO
    --scenario SCENARIO           (see: ai help wizard scenario)

`SCENARIOS`

  Chat (OpenAI)
  Chat w/ your prompt (OpenAI)
  Chat w/ your data (OpenAI)
  Caption audio (Speech to Text)
  Caption images and video (Vision)
  Extract text from images (Vision)
  Extract text from documents and forms (Language)
  Transcribe and analyze calls (Speech, Language)
  Translate documents and text (Language)
  Summarize documents (Language)
  ...more!        

